Funding-Text = {A special thanks to the staff and curators at A, BM, GH, HN, HNU, K, L,
   MO, MT, NY, P, and hlnp who `` rolled out the red carpet{''} and helped
   to make our visits to these herbaria so enjoyable and productive. We are
   also grateful to Shuren Zhang for providing specimen photographs and
   answering numerous questions related to the collections in PE. Bobbi
